{"tid":1564222,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[毋忘721] 港人球迷914對抗元朗白色恐怖","createTime":"2019-09-12T16:26:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T10:23:29.000Z","uid":199,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a24f51ede85fee0276bd605f9a487bed0e855214","tid":1564222,"uid":199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:26:04.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">721元朗黑夜</span> <span style=\"color: limegreen;\">追究到底</span><span style=\"color: maroon;\">對抗白色恐怖</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CrrwJ9J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCrrwJ9J.jpg&h=1ef1c8e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CpMdc23.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCpMdc23.jpg&h=ad064a6b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n7月21日 元朗黑夜 歷歷在目<br />\n<br />\n數百名白衣人在元朗西鐵站無差別襲擊市民，元朗區議員王威信懷疑牽涉其中，導致45名市民受傷，數名市民更是情況嚴重及危殆。<br />\n<br />\n事後，警方承認<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">收到報案後39分鐘</span></ins></span>才到達現場，鐵路應變部隊仍未有出動。元朗警區助理指揮官更表示未見有任何白衣人持有武器。<br />\n<br />\n香港一直為安全城市引以為傲，如今發生如此暴力事件實在令市民不能接受。一連串巧合亦令我們懷疑警方或一干人等均有預謀地策劃上述事件，更是令人髮指。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">為此，我們發起在球賽第21分鐘全場靜立，強烈譴責警方的處理手法，以及白衣人和一干人等的暴力事件。歡迎各位有心人於賽事當日來到球場26區觀眾席集合，以和平理性手法表達訴求。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">傑志vs元朗<br />\n日期：9月14日（星期六）<br />\n地點：旺角大球場<br />\n時間：下午5:30</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">備註：市民可自行穿上黑色上衣或者印上7/21號的球衣，帶備口罩和頭盔。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"88644a24f1e5a77832ffa944d72e6ec729f3e3ac","tid":1564222,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:26:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"95555bffb7a280827e140722182c1fdf879bd4df","tid":1564222,"uid":199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:39:32.000Z","msg":"PUSH<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bd584008eb0cae75394646ef50e4994beba1ebc","tid":1564222,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T16:43:24.000Z","msg":"有無尿國文賽程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc6bb5f671e0cdbb2eb0e7d2cbf3a91b7ae6c241","tid":1564222,"uid":33053,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T17:30:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n元朗足球會會長﹐元朗區議員兼元朗區議會副主席，經民聯成員王威信721開閘幫白衣人入元朗站打人</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z2gMvNN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz2gMvNN.gif&h=f31728d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dj33x2Z.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDj33x2Z.gif&h=a355fadd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190722/s00001/f2c9b73df0d0a714de2554d1bce7ce64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190722%2Fs00001%2Ff2c9b73df0d0a714de2554d1bce7ce64.jpg&h=bc9fa25c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"70fbf068c0a9db463f33e57663b6b1a1ae82eb1c","tid":1564222,"uid":19847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply